sources.description:
When John Masonâ€™s father is killed, John is wounded. Attracted to his nurse Alice, a conflict arises between him and his friend Ben who plans to marry Alice. John later finds the killer of his father but goes to face him not knowing Ben has removed the bullets from his gun.

Directed by Robert N. Bradbury
Alternative Title: Cold Vengeance (1935)

Colorized version: https://youtu.be/RC9XEloPvnU

Cast:
John Wayne as John Mason
Marion Burns as Alice Gordon
Dennis Moore as Rudd Gordon
Reed Howes as Ben McClure
Joseph De Grasse as Dad Mason
Yakima Canutt as Saloon Owner
Earl Dwire as Pete (Expressman)
Nelson McDowell as Bates (Undertaker)
Genres: Western, Action, Adventure
